<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-43-0762 </DOCNO><TEXT>The principle areas of building services energy cost reduction availablewith advanced control systems are reviewed and also the UK experienceof such systems. The experience of the Department of Energy's EfficiencyDemonstration Scheme (EEDS) gained in supporting the implementation ofEnergy Management Systems for medium size and small sites, and also fordistributed sites linked by automatic telephone dialling is outlined.The extent to which the UK has become a world leader in microprocessor-basedEnergy Management Technology is made clear.</TEXT></DOC>